Revision history for Perl extension SchemaView Plus.

0.17 <20140118>
	- put Math::Project, Data::CompactDump to separate CPAN distribution
	- remove Data::RefSupport (obsolete with List::Flatten)

0.16 <20020121>
	- removing test for XML::SimpleParser

0.15 <20020111>
	- PostScript::Poster instead of standalone poster

0.14 <20011127>
	- DBIx::SystemCatalog::XBase - fs_ls() implementation
	- DBIx::SystemCatalog used for dbsh - fs_ls()
	- Data::CompactDump output format - export, loading with autodetecting
	- stop working on XML::SimpleParser - bad way
	- new betatester Muller
	- founded new bugs, enlarging todo
	- start working on PostScript::Poster
	- MANIFEST.SKIP
	- DBIx::SystemCatalog::Oracle support for unique and indexes

0.13 <20011113>
	- finding objects in object repository
	- edit relationship
	- create relationship

0.12 <20011111>
	- new about box
	- splash
	- setting program name for ps/top structures
	- support for printing to Ghostview (gv) and printer
	- Print::Printcap interface to /etc/printcap
	- changing order in edit table dialog changed from drag to button
	- constant size of Place button
	- showing PK in more information dialog
	- don't uppercase table name in rename and new object
	- setting PK in edit table dialog
	- in edit table dialog don't uppercase added items
	- retrieve overwrites objects in Object repository
		(but forgot all new informations)
	- don't store retrieve_ items from previous versions
	- filters in retrieving dialog
	- memorize connection information in retrieve schema
	- optionable extra information in Object repository
	- correcting bug with Object repository showing
	- DBIx::SystemCatalog indexes and unique indexes support
	- showing PK in edit table dialog
	- some new hints
	- postering support
	- PostScript printing options (limits, rotation) (Luf)
	- saving and restoring selected font in *.svp files
	- changing font on canvas (Luf), need Tk::FontDialog
	- DBIx::SystemCatalog::Pg made by Luf
	- showing primary keys in tables
	- add line between table name and table columns
	- retrieve primary keys
	- new about box dialog
	- DBIx::SystemCatalog::Pg support for relationships (thanks to Luf)
	- correct bug with dropping unplaced objects
	- small changes in GUI

0.11 <20010420>
	- Data::RefSupport
	- start working on XML::SimpleParser
	- announcing on Freshmeat

0.10 <20010419>
	- multiple columns relationships support
	- little corrections in putting and dropping dragpoints in smooth curve
	- correct bug with empty object repository
	- new table or view in repository
	- edit table or view in repository
	- rename table, view or relationship in repository
	- changing order of items in edit table
	- new file and object repository if we start svplus without arguments

